works.description: http://www.TheHerbFinder.com landing page and throughout the site-map my graphics appear on and off again depending on the administrator Shawnvs@gmail.com. The Header displays moving gif images of a variety of plants, you can see how they have taken my original work and duplicated it so the header fills the table; furthermore there are leaves appearing next to their title "The Herb Finder" in an ellipse that is taken from a logo currently licensed elsewhere. Also the background of the site is part of the already licensed logo mentioned below.

copyrighted_urls.url: http://www.Totalherbalhealth.com The Box Flowers.gif is not currently available anywhere other than your image search however if you look at www.TotalHerbalHealth.com you can see their logo is from the exact same file as the ellipse and image text. The Box Flower header is taken 100% from my image file, I'm certain it is even present in the detail/property information of the image. I can provide the original document if necessary.
